To invoke a method, one requires a variable that points to an object (e.g., only given a variable like `o` can one call a method: `o.m()`).

frontmatter.shortDescription: One needs a variable to invoke a method
frontmatter.shortCorrection: Methods can be invoked on expressions that evaluate to a suitable object
